{"tid":1888451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB化妝師於鑽石公主號確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-02-20T08:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T11:53:23.000Z","uid":199893,"like":823,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea9b1c4ba8a48370c783d58c0545acdd8d9a145","tid":1888451,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐，香港累計確診或增至67宗，而處於日本的鑽石公主號郵至今有621人染疫。今日《蘋果》收到消息，指有無綫員工確診患上武漢肺炎，據知該名員工是鑽石公主號郵輪乘客，多日來被困船上，連日來的無綫新聞，亦有以電話訪問方式向該員工直擊船上情況。<br />\n<br />\n李寶安回應《蘋果》：「鑽石公主號上其中一名確診女患者為本台化妝師，她今曰（20日）通知公司說早上被確診，現正於日本接受治療。她自1月25日開始休假至今。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200220&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=60621021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200220%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D60621021&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=f8d612a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200220%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D60621021&h=6270fcb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200220&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=60621021</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5239ecf84c24b3996bb20b2f41109c194114d73b","tid":1888451,"uid":199893,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"天有眼"},{"pid":"c59a93be51f25bce854e5047f90bece404196072","tid":1888451,"uid":77092,"like":179,"dislike":5,"score":174,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:11:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d384795593c0d28256a6d3502d817556421f691","tid":1888451,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3fb19e81693f998dd3273807f0db3ff6f443539","tid":1888451,"uid":199893,"like":51,"dislik